      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROBOT GIRL (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (18.43) last time in a Maiden at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Better than last start and worth following up. MISCHIEF AFOOT (3) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 6 length second (17.80) over 300m at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Expected to feature again. RADIANT MISS (1) shows ability but remains a maiden after 23 starts. Is better than last start when out of the placings, finishing fourth (18.15) at this track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can do much better this time. NEVER CHANGE (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
